entries.title_d: The Rebels have sent out a strike team in retaliation for the loss of their scout. Destroy all the Rebel fighters.
entries.title: Endor System: Rebel Counterstrike
entries.split_quest_alert: Scans of Rebel transmissions indicate Rebel communications ship nearby your location. Disable vessel and recover any information from its computers that you can. Stand by for nav location.
entries.complete: You have survived the surprise attack!
